Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: cloudflare-utils
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-pip, ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}
Description: Cloudflare DNS Update Utility
  A set of utilities to interact with Cloudflare DNS records, allowing for
  automated updates of DNS records using a specified set of IP addresses.
  .
  This tool can be run manually via CLI, or set up to run periodically
  using cron or systemd timers. It uses a .env file for configuration
  and provides logging for its operations.
